{"tid":1713733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[打工仔心聲] 聽朝同我一樣要返工既，麻煩入一入黎。","createTime":"2019-11-12T19:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T00:52:48.000Z","uid":167177,"like":86,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"8c386166741b6fb5556b43723db05f467f269b30","tid":1713733,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:12:16.000Z","msg":"我係一個無錢、搵得少、有家庭負擔同餐搵餐食既打工仔。<br />\n<br />\n係香港物價奇高下生活，我怕無錢；<br />\n同畢了業同學比較人工，我怕搵得少；<br />\n家有老邁父母要養之下，我怕畀唔夠家用。<br />\n所以我好怕罷工，因為手停口停。<br />\n<br />\n你地可以話我係一個只會用口去支持自由的和理非。<br />\n我覺成日覺得用口去聲討就夠，因為總有人會出錢，有人會出力，少我一個咪一個囉。<br />\n無傷大雅。<br />\n<br />\n有浮屍？我會同同事send句好嬲。<br />\n有跳樓？我會同同學send句好憤怒。<br />\n有人被殺？我會向朋友send句要報仇。<br />\n<br />\n然後？<br />\n沒然後了。<br />\n因為我覺得我用文字發了聲，便對得起我良心，較心安理得。<br />\n<br />\n直到今日看見各大學被圍城攻打，同學便堅守自己的大學。<br />\n佢地個種就算面對邪惡政權同軍隊，仍然義無反顧咁去守護校園，守衛自己的初心。<br />\n學生離邪惡的距離之遠，令我呢位一直只顧返工，不理世事的人感到非常自責。<br />\n<br />\n我發覺良心的責備，並唔係用藉口就可以安撫到。<br />\n要返工的你，有無同樣湧到上心口的自責愧疚感？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所以我決定聽日罷工</strong></span></span>，<br />\n去用自己微不足道的力量去支持學生同正義。<br />\n對於罷工，正常打工仔都有有薪sick leave。<br />\n要上班的你，又有無呢個決心，去支持一下班細路？"},{"pid":"255eff3ce231cd627c925562d184cb79a9ae52a5","tid":1713733,"uid":30423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:13:06.000Z","msg":"推 香港人加油！"},{"pid":"79be68deb5b28c36b04a9036408e24e61d833a8c","tid":1713733,"uid":308682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:13:14.000Z","msg":"推唔郁都要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40db6c9fbe15758d3f821e352fa1df181d0a3ea","tid":1713733,"uid":302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-F30JwBRK7rI/WWsi2eIc2GI/AAAAAAAAASs/QRs1iYXrLoQ4asj6CNFVIBnSt8EuHbVjACLcBGAs/s1600/BmPJIbnIIAEWNTK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-F30JwBRK7rI%2FWWsi2eIc2GI%2FAAAAAAAAASs%2FQRs1iYXrLoQ4asj6CNFVIBnSt8EuHbVjACLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2FBmPJIbnIIAEWNTK.jpg&h=dd355f33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果跟到呢幾步做 就好大機會贏返少少<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713666\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713666</a>"},{"pid":"3d6452d6fb852bed52f2108049e0ab70395dc581","tid":1713733,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:14:19.000Z","msg":"推幾下"},{"pid":"cf480c447cbfd20d5102c5f74e46b405165e6f67","tid":1713733,"uid":306541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:19:09.000Z","msg":"(千其唔好玩水！！）我係一個有十年經驗嘅消防系統嘅人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713673</a>"},{"pid":"9ce928ea9c695c89f0039f301b480a757cff1e4a","tid":1713733,"uid":23343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:19:29.000Z","msg":"真香港人"},{"pid":"980201d3556592734497d90d400dc428932b90b6","tid":1713733,"uid":167177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:19:46.000Z","msg":"各位可以幫我聽日7點左右幫我推上去畀D要返工既人睇下？"},{"pid":"420ad5f274b9ba156437f09ff7fe9840dfc44ca8","tid":1713733,"uid":178527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:20:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8daeb81a3fb4861776b75066adbf29d839424d9f","tid":1713733,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:20:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c0f5869dc123863db994be0dfc273c17b5fd7dc1","tid":1713733,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:21:04.000Z","msg":"好<br />\n承先賢之志<br />\n燃革命之火"},{"pid":"8a76b5b4c113c22439f50b464b0eee48821b1e39","tid":1713733,"uid":14566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:22:56.000Z","msg":"真係唔夠錢洗 大把香港人幫你"},{"pid":"3dce7422be6c4cf91db03e39fec1e5f9253a99c3","tid":1713733,"uid":171573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:24:59.000Z","msg":"多謝你手足<br />\n香港人，報仇"},{"pid":"eee8108c41cc1df9baf6a2fbd5419f4830fa3fc3","tid":1713733,"uid":260654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3d6452d6fb852bed52f2108049e0ab70395dc581","tid":1713733,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:14:19.000Z","msg":"推幾下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:26:46.000Z","msg":"唔好罷，早啲起身番工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先可以幫手塞鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752086331c94af71e783cc2d9a97c1b94d961e29","tid":1713733,"uid":153239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:27:54.000Z","msg":"我銀行都無乜幾蚊, 同埋有同事長假<br />\n所以我聽日用上午清哂D野, 下午買野入中大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7520eac8a8abe403842da9dda65db6b60bc9719","tid":1713733,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:28:58.000Z","msg":"其實罷工後去買D物資，出下力都好"},{"pid":"3800ca449173d8f7cd55898b0975fdf7cf97353d","tid":1713733,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:29:50.000Z","msg":"有力出力 有錢出錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0ed4eee16cc8643e906de04ae4625127d90fdd","tid":1713733,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:30:36.000Z","msg":"三罷，係罷工罷課罷市<br />\n唔該聽日決定唔返工嘅人，同樣要唔消費<br />\n咁先係做到一片蕭條嘅景象"},{"pid":"94e010deaa454d9b98b6267102e650fc88527e84","tid":1713733,"uid":275613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:30:43.000Z","msg":"我地要頂住啊<br />\n我今日工都 辭埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5464eb23c70e9a7191258cbec78cd5b3ab0b6d8","tid":1713733,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgm